    h1 User Management API
    p Welcome to the User Management API. This API allows you to manage users, including creating, updating, and deleting user accounts.
    p To get started, you can use the following endpoints:
    ul
      li GET /users - Retrieve a list of all users
      li POST /users - Create a new user
      li GET /users/:id - Retrieve a specific user by ID
      li PUT /users/:id - Update a specific user by ID
      li DELETE /users/:id - Delete a specific user by ID
    p For more information, please refer to the API documentation.